Examples

in:devices
in:alerts
in:activity
in:auditLog

Example

in:devices after:2022-03-10

Example

in:alerts after:2022-03-11T14:00:00 before:2022-03-16T14:00:00

Example

in:auditLog timeFrame:"7 Days" user:"John"
